            â€¢ **Widget 3 Peak req/min** â†’ set initial WAF rate limits (use ~2â€“3Ã— peak).  
            â€¢ **Widget 5 Error Totals** â†’ watch for increases after enabling WAF.  
            â€¢ **Widget 1 EB Health** â†’ ensure app stability throughout.
          EOT
        }
      }
    ]
  })
}

